text: Johnny Doughboy is a 1942 American musical comedy movie directed by John H. Auer and starring Jane Withers, Henry Wilcoxon, William Demarest, Ruth Donnelly, Etta McDaniel, Bobby Breen. It was distributed by Republic Pictures and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1943. ==Other websites== * Category:1942 comedy movies Category:1940s American musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by John H. Auer
